data.description: As you enter, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living room seamlessly connected to the dining area, creating the perfect space for gatherings. The kitchen features a large stainless steel farmhouse sink, ss appliances and plenty of counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. The true gem of this home is the primary suite. It's generously sized, with a walk-in closet that provides ample storage for your wardrobe. The primary bathroom is a sanctuary in itself, offering a soaker tub for those relaxing soak sessions, a stand-up shower for a quick and refreshing start to your day, and dual vanities for added convenience. Step outside to the spacious backyard, where you'll find low-maintenance artificial grass that always looks lush and green, ensuring your outdoor space remains pristine year-round. Offering plenty of room for outdoor activities and entertainment. This home is more than just a house; it's a haven of comfort and modern elegance. Don't miss the opportunity!
